  "title": "Desktop and Systems Management The HP Way: Using Open Standards To Lower Costs and Complexity",
  "description": "Aberdeen Group strategy profile examining HP's use of the Desktop Management Interface (DMI) standard in its Vectra Corporate PC line and TopTOOLS management software. Aberdeen argues HP's open-standards approach positions it to overtake Compaq in enterprise PC sales, and that DMI certification will become a de facto standard for desktop management cost reduction.",
